(496, 1, '2008-04-06 10:39:24', '2008-04-06 15:39:24', 'Trying to plan a trip to Europe is HARD!  Man, unless you know exactly what you want to do or have plenty of cash to drop, it''s a mega-headache.  All these options are overwhelming.\r\n\r\nNow I''m thinking I should just visit a travel agent but what a cop out.  I must resist...', 'Europe Planning', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'europe-planning', '', '', '2008-04-06 10:39:24', '2008-04-06 15:39:24', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=496', 0, 'post', '', 3),
(2, 1, '2008-03-24 09:20:54', '2008-03-24 14:20:54', 'Hi there! I was born in Winnipeg and I have resided in Ottawa, Canada for most of his life. I am currently wrapping up my degree in <a href="http://www.sce.carleton.ca/dept/about/index.shtml">Systems and Computer Engineering</a> at <a href="http://carleton.ca/">Carleton University</a> also in Ottawa, Canada.  In my spare time I spend my time playing <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ultimate_Frisbee">Ultimate</a>, enjoying a wide variety of beer with friends, playing guitar, calling <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/CQ_%28call%29">CQ</a>, expanding my creativity using photography, becoming a <a href="http://loversofgod.com/EN/whoweare.htm">lover of God</a> and making him known, and playing with various forms of technology.  My interests or the technological side mainly lay in <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Embedded_systems">embedded systems</a> and <a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Digital_Signal_Processing">digital signal processing</a>.\r\n<h2>About This Site</h2>\r\nI have been playing with the web for many years. When I was 13 I started my own web design and hosting business. That company has pretty vanished but I still enjoy having a website to express my thoughts and creativity. Below are some pictures from some previous versions of my site.', 'About', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'about', '', '', '2008-05-19 10:37:33', '2008-05-19 15:37:33', '', 0, '', 0, 'page', '', 0),
