(7, 1, '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', 'In general, I try to be as organized and efficient as possible.  Especially when I''m working or trying to get things done.  Here are some ways I do that:\n<ul>\n	<li>Ditch digital calendars for paper - </li>\n	<li>Use the keyboard instead of the mouse -</li>\n	<li>If it takes less than two minutes, just do it now!</li>\n	<li>Record everything you need to do down.  So much energy is spent just trying to remember the things that need to get done - I use virtual stickies.</li>\n</ul>', 'Productivity Thoughts', 0, '', 'draft', 'open', 'open', '', '', '', '', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '0000-00-00 00:00:00', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=7', 0, 'post', '', 0),
