(156, 1, '2005-10-28 23:23:37', '2005-10-29 04:23:37', 'Went to Starbucks with a bunch of my friends to start up a bible study for the rest of the semester that will hopefully continue through next semester.  I showed up and ordered my Grande Hot Chocolate:\n<blockquote>\nJevy: Hiya Kin!  Whatcha get?\nKin: Hot Chocolate.\nJevy: Seriously?  That''s what I got.\n*We go sit down as Dan walks in and orders*\nDan: Hey guys!\nK and J: Word\nDan: What did you guys order?\nK and J: Hot Chocolate\nDan: HAHA.  Me too.\n* Travvy walks in... and orders nothing*\n</blockquote>\nAnyways, we thought it was funny enough.  Who orders hot chocolate??  Then we met up with the CRU gang and watched and watched "Les Choristes".  See above.', 'Hot Chocolate and Cl', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'hot-chocolate-and-clement-mathieu', '', '', '2005-10-28 23:23:37', '2005-10-29 04:23:37', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=156', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(157, 1, '2005-10-28 23:34:57', '2005-10-29 04:34:57', '<img src="http://jevy.org/random/wp/68m.jpg" width="97" height="140" alt="Les Choristes" title="" align=left /> Dan C needed to log two hours for his french class (?) so he suggested we rent a "real" french movie.  So off to Blockbuster we went.  <a href="http://www.livejournal.com/users/travy_pp/">Travy</a> picked the winner tonight.  With a seemingly random "Les Choristes".  Turns out to be awesome!  The ladies were giggling and "aww"ing the entire way through and the guys were laughing for sure!  A simple heart warming experience.\n\nCross between <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0097165/">Dead Poets Society</a> and <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0113862/">Mr. Holland''s Opus</a>.  With a bit of an open end which I always love. 4.5/5', 'Les Choristes', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'les-choristes', '', '', '2005-10-28 23:34:57', '2005-10-29 04:34:57', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=157', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(158, 1, '2005-10-29 13:01:49', '2005-10-29 18:01:49', 'Ott to TO/Guelph (Round Trip)\n\nLeaving from Carleton Thursday, Nov 10th at 5:30pm.  Drop off in TO/Mississauga is flexible but close to the 401 would be nice.  Returning the afternoon of Sunday, Nov 13th.\n\nI''m pretty unsure of my own plans so we can work stuff out.  I wanted to offer it to jevy.org and livejournal readers first before I post on the ott.rides newsgroup.  I''ll let you know how much gas will be but of course that depends on how many come.  I can take 4 plus 1 on the roof.  If you take the roof, you get a discount on gas.  I cruise at 115km/h since this matters to some people.\n\nRequirements for the ride:\n<ul>\n	<li>Bladder must be able to handle stopping for rest stops no more than 10 times.</li>\n<li>Must stink less than a wet dog</li>\n	<li>Easy going with music selection as I might just whip out some Justin Timberlake and Salt and Peppaaaaaaa.  Uhh.. but I won''t so don''t worry</li>\n	<li>Be cool if we don''t feel like talking the entire way.</li>\n</ul>\n\nLet me know', 'Ride Offer', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'ride-offer', '', '', '2005-10-29 13:01:49', '2005-10-29 18:01:49', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=158', 0, 'post', '', 3),
