(188, 1, '2005-12-17 22:03:39', '2005-12-18 03:03:39', '.. Dirty Vegas.  That was a great song.  But really the reason for this post:\n\nDear Lord,\nIt''s all flying by.  Nearly too fast.  How do I enjoy every minute?!  Don''t let a day pass me by without knowing that today I did your will.  Then, on days where my shortsightedness blinds my heart... I can stand.\nYour "blah"ed out son,\nJevin', 'Days go by..', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'days-go-by', '', '', '2005-12-17 22:03:39', '2005-12-18 03:03:39', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=188', 0, 'post', '', 0),
(189, 1, '2005-12-19 11:46:44', '2005-12-19 16:46:44', 'Holy crap.  I Skyped up Chan to ask about some equations for Quantum I didn''t get:\n\n<blockquote>\nJevy: Hey man.  What''s the S.E equation and solution for tunnelling?\nBew: I don''t know man.  I''m studying networking.\nJevy: Whoa!  You feel that good about Quantum that you can study for tomorrow''s exam when we have Quantum today?\nBew: WHAT???  We have Quantum tomorrow!\nJevy: WHAT?!!??!?! Quantum''s today!  Stop lying\nBew: No man..\nJevy: WHAT?!?!  I''m sweating everywhere. AHHHHHH\nBew: AHHHH I''m shaking for you.  Let''s go to school.  I''ll teach you everything!\nJevy: AHHHHHHHH\n.. and here we are. With two hours before an exam I''m barely studied for.  WHAAA\n</blockquote>\n\n<strong>Update</strong>:  Turned out to be fine.  Now I''m ready for tomorrow''s exam :)  I think God lead me to talk to Chan today.  Otherwise I would have been stinking lost', 'Day from hell God', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'day-from-hell-god', '', '', '2005-12-19 11:46:44', '2005-12-19 16:46:44', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=189', 0, 'post', '', 3),
