(235, 1, '2006-03-01 20:46:05', '2006-03-02 01:46:05', '<a class="imagelink" title="My Messy Desktop" onclick="doPopup(267);return false;" href="http://jevy.org/wp-content/uploads/2006/03/Messy%20Desktop.jpg"><img width="128" height="96" class="alignright" id="image267" alt="My Messy Desktop" src="http://jevy.org/wp-content/uploads/2006/03/Messy%20Desktop.thumbnail.jpg" /></a>Life right now is bonkers.  If you don''t believe me, check out my not so tidy (anymore) desktop.  Maybe I''ll have time to clean ''er up on the weekend.\n\nI wonder if most people really feel like they don''t have things in place.  I mean, I can deal with the openendedness (is that a word?) but it''s just having things hanging over my head (either good or bad) that really add to well.. this tension in my neck.', 'It&#8217;s a mess', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'its-a-mess', '', '', '2006-03-01 20:46:05', '2006-03-02 01:46:05', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=235', 0, 'post', '', 2),
(236, 1, '2006-03-02 22:33:35', '2006-03-03 03:33:35', '<strong>Sorry if this doesn''t make sense.  It''s mainly for me.</strong>\n<ol>\n	<li>4pm - My family got together with my former pastor and his family today.</li>\n	<li>They talked about their plans</li>\n	<li>My parents talked about how much they learned from them.  They prayed for them.</li>\n	<li>I shared about how I will cherish the four years I have been built into by him.  He cried.  He pleaded that I would not remember him as a sinful man.  I wept.  He said Jesus will never let me down even if he had.  He was a wreck by now.  I wept some more.</li>\n	<li>My brother said how much he has learned in the short time being at the church.</li>\n	<li>They thanked us for coming by and we all hugged and sorta said our goodbyes.</li>\n	<li>They called at 9:45 to say how much us gonig over there meant to them.</li>\n	<li>They leave on Saturday.  Forever :(</li>\n</ol>', 'Hardest day of March 2006', 0, '', 'publish', 'closed', 'open', '', 'hardest-day-of-march-2006', '', '', '2006-03-02 22:33:35', '2006-03-03 03:33:35', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=236', 0, 'post', '', 0),
