(437, 1, '2007-04-09 13:08:38', '2007-04-09 20:08:38', '<a href=''http://jevy.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/04/10m.jpg'' title=''Children of Men''><img src=''http://jevy.org/wp-content/uploads/2007/04/10m.jpg'' alt=''Children of Men'' /></a>On a day where I am supposed to be studying for exams (whatever.. we''re good), I decided to watch <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0206634/">Children of Men</a>.  Wow!  Talk about not what you expected.  I felt this movie was mainly a commentary on society today and the direction where we will be heading.  It was suspenseful the entire way through but left a lot of (unimportant?) questions unanswered.  I''m trying to be intensionally vague without giving any of it away.  It''s a beautiful, dark movie about fighting for what is right.  Check it out!', 'Children of Men', 0, '', 'publish', 'open', 'open', '', 'children-of-men', '', '', '2007-04-09 13:08:38', '2007-04-09 20:08:38', '', 0, 'http://jevy.org/?p=437', 0, 'post', '', 0),
